      <title>韩国议会批准禁止吃狗肉的法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-09/ap-newsalert-south-korea-s-parliament-has-endorsed-landmark-legislation-outlawing-dog-meat-consumption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国首尔（美联社）——韩国议会批准了具有里程碑意义的立法，禁止食用狗肉。]]></description>
