      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/thai-premier-to-meet-with-central-bank-governor-amid-clamor-for-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 表示，他将于周三会见泰国央行行长 Sethaput Suthiwartnarueput，讨论一系列问题，一天前，他敦促央行考虑降低利率。]]></description>
