      <title>五角大楼因国防部长奥斯汀缺席而面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/pentagon-under-pressure-over-defense-secretary-austin-s-absence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀四天没有通知白宫有关他住院的情况后，美国议员要求五角大楼做出答复，称他们对他缺席的解释不满意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/pentagon-under-pressure-over-defense-secretary-austin-s-absence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 00:07:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里领导人警告他将反对埃塞俄比亚红海计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/somalia-leader-warns-he-will-fight-against-ethiopia-red-sea-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里总统哈桑·谢赫·马哈茂德警告邻国埃塞俄比亚，如果埃塞俄比亚在确保经由索马里分离地区索马里兰直接进入红海方面取得进展，他将采取“一切必要措施”保卫国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/somalia-leader-warns-he-will-fight-against-ethiopia-red-sea-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 13:56:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
